steps.html_instructions:
Turn left onto Epar.Od. Livadochoriou-Karpasio/Epar.Od. Mirina-Moudrou
Continue to follow Epar.Od. Mirina-Moudrou

Posidonos turns left and becomes Ilia Iliou
Go through 2 roundabouts

Take the Kavala - Limnos ferry to Καβάλα
Toll road

Continue straight
Partial restricted usage road
At the roundabout, take the 1st exit onto Erithrou Stavrou/EO2

Turn left to merge onto Egnatia Odos/EO Thessalonikis-Kavalas/A2/E90 toward θεσσαλονίκν/Thessaloniki
Toll road

Take the exit on the left onto A/D Pireos Athinon Thessalonikis Evzonon/Egnatia Odos/A1/A2/E90 toward ATHINA/VEROIA/E75
Toll road
Turn right onto Epar.Od. Asfaka - Vrisochoriou (signs for Vikos Gorge/Central Zagori)
Turn right to stay on Epar.Od. Asfaka - Vrisochoriou (signs for Dilofo)
Turn left to stay on Epar.Od. Asfaka - Vrisochoriou
